            <!-- Stemmatics -->
            <note type="stemmatics">Two mss. cited by OY, including Veliyuddin 1821 which our inspection shows to be unattributed to IA. In its current form it is unlikely to be by IA as in FM he does not use the term al-mawjūd al-muṭlaq, only al-wujūd al-muṭlaq (eg FM 1:44, 76, 365, 718 etc ), and the phrase al-durra al-bayḍāʾ occurs only twice (FM 1:46, 2:30) (SH). Further work needed.</note>
